{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"WebSocket","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/binaryType\"><code>binaryType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/bufferedAmount\"><code>bufferedAmount</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/extensions\"><code>extensions</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/protocol\"><code>protocol</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/url\"><code>url</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/send\"><code>send()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close_event\"><code>close</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/error_event\"><code>error</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event\"><code>message</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event\"><code>open</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><code>WebSocket</code>&nbsp;对象提供了用于创建和管理&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSockets_API\" title=\"zh-CN/WebSockets\">WebSocket</a>&nbsp;连接，以及可以通过该连接发送和接收数据的 API。</p>\n\n<p>使用<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/WebSocket\"> WebSocket()</a></code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/WebSocket\"> </a>构造函数来构造一个<code> WebSocket</code> 。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"构造函数","title":"构造函数","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"websocketurl_protocols\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/WebSocket\" title=\"WebSocket(url[, protocols])\"><code>WebSocket(url[, protocols])</code></a></dt>\n <dd>返回一个&nbsp;<code>WebSocket</code> 对象。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"常量","title":"常量","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><strong>Constant</strong></td>\n   <td><strong>Value</strong></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>WebSocket.CONNECTING</code></td>\n   <td><code>0</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>WebSocket.OPEN</code></td>\n   <td><code>1</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>WebSocket.CLOSING</code></td>\n   <td><code>2</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>WebSocket.CLOSED</code></td>\n   <td><code>3</code></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"websocket.binarytype\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/binaryType\"><code>WebSocket.binaryType</code></a></dt>\n <dd>使用二进制的数据类型连接。</dd>\n <dt id=\"websocket.bufferedamount\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/bufferedAmount\"><code>WebSocket.bufferedAmount</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>未发送至服务器的字节数。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"websocket.extensions\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/extensions\"><code>WebSocket.extensions</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>服务器选择的扩展。</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"websocket.onclose\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close_event\"><code>WebSocket.onclose</code></a></dt>\n <dd>用于指定连接关闭后的回调函数。</dd>\n <dt id=\"websocket.onerror\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/WebSocket/error_event\"><code>WebSocket.onerror</code></a></dt>\n <dd>用于指定连接失败后的回调函数。</dd>\n <dt id=\"websocket.onmessage\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event\"><code>WebSocket.onmessage</code></a></dt>\n <dd>用于指定当从服务器接受到信息时的回调函数。</dd>\n <dt id=\"websocket.onopen\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event\"><code>WebSocket.onopen</code></a></dt>\n <dd>用于指定连接成功后的回调函数。</dd>\n <dt id=\"websocket.protocol\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/protocol\"><code>WebSocket.protocol</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>服务器选择的下属协议。</dd>\n <dt id=\"websocket.readystate\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/readyState\"><code>WebSocket.readyState</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>当前的链接状态。</dd>\n <dt id=\"websocket.url\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/url\"><code>WebSocket.url</code></a> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>WebSocket 的绝对路径。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"method_overview","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"websocket.closecode_reason\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close\" title=\"WebSocket.close([code[, reason]])\"><code>WebSocket.close([code[, reason]])</code></a></dt>\n <dd>关闭当前链接。</dd>\n <dt id=\"websocket.senddata\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/send\" title=\"WebSocket.send(data)\"><code>WebSocket.send(data)</code></a></dt>\n <dd>对要传输的数据进行排队。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"事件","title":"事件","isH3":false,"content":"<p>使用 <code>addEventListener()</code> 或将一个事件监听器赋值给本接口的&nbsp;<code>on<em>eventname</em></code> 属性，来监听下面的事件。</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"close\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close_event\" title=\"close\"><code>close</code></a></dt>\n <dd>当一个&nbsp;<code>WebSocket</code>&nbsp;连接被关闭时触发。<br>\n 也可以通过 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close_event\" title=\"onclose\"><code>onclose</code></a> 属性来设置。</dd>\n <dt id=\"error\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/error_event\" title=\"error\"><code>error</code></a></dt>\n <dd>当一个&nbsp;<code>WebSocket</code>&nbsp;连接因错误而关闭时触发，例如无法发送数据时。<br>\n 也可以通过 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/WebSocket/error_event\" title=\"onerror\"><code>onerror</code></a> 属性来设置。</dd>\n <dt id=\"message\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event\" title=\"message\"><code>message</code></a></dt>\n <dd>当通过&nbsp;<code>WebSocket</code>&nbsp;收到数据时触发。<br>\n 也可以通过 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event\" title=\"onmessage\"><code>onmessage</code></a> 属性来设置。</dd>\n <dt id=\"open\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event\" title=\"open\"><code>open</code></a></dt>\n <dd>当一个&nbsp;<code>WebSocket</code>&nbsp;连接成功时触发。<br>\n 也可以通过 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event\" title=\"onopen\"><code>onopen</code></a> 属性来设置。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributes","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js line-numbers language-js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Create WebSocket connection.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> socket <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">WebSocket</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'ws://localhost:8080'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Connection opened</span>\nsocket<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'open'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    socket<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">send</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello Server!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Listen for messages</span>\nsocket<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'message'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Message from server '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/web-sockets.html#the-websocket-interface","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.WebSocket"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.WebSocket","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSockets_API/Writing_WebSocket_client_applications\" title=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSockets_API/Writing_WebSocket_client_applications\">Writing WebSocket client applications</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"构造函数","id":"构造函数"},{"text":"常量","id":"常量"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"method_overview"},{"text":"事件","id":"事件"},{"text":"示例","id":"attributes"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"WebSocket 对象提供了用于创建和管理 WebSocket 连接，以及可以通过该连接发送和接收数据的 API。","popularity":0.0059,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebSocket","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"WebSocket","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebSocket","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"WebSocket","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebSocket","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WebSocket","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WebSocket","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"WebSocket","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"WebSocket","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/websocket","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/websocket/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/WebSocket","title":"WebSocket"}],"pageTitle":"WebSocket - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}